Push through your heels to return to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-heels-up-front-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-heels-up-front-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Barbell Lateral Lunge', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a barbell at your shoulders with an overhand grip.
