Push off your right foot to return to the starting position.
Repeat on the opposite side by stepping out with your left foot.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-lateral-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-lateral-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Barbell Pause Box Squat', 'Stand in front of a box or bench with your feet shoulder-width apart and a barbell resting on your upper back.
