Push through your heels to return to the standing position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-pause-box-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-pause-box-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Barbell Pause Squat', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and a barbell resting on your upper back.
