Push through your heels to return to the standing position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-pause-box-squat-front_GEhqEjs.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-pause-box-squat-side_2PFhPFu.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Barbell Reverse Deadlift', 'Start by standing with your feet about hip-width apart, with your toes pointed slightly outward.
