Push off your back foot, returning to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-reverse-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-reverse-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Bodyweight Reverse Step Up', 'Start with a box or bench behind you and one of your feet on the box/bench.
