Step back down with your right foot, lowering your left foot to the ground.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-step-up-balance-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-step-up-balance-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Barbell Step Up', 'Begin by standing in front of a sturdy box or bench that is about knee-height, holding a barbell across your upper back and shoulders, using an overhand grip.
