Push through your heels to extend your hips and stand up, bringing your body back to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-tap-box-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-tap-box-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Barbell Zercher Squat', 'Begin by standing with your feet about hip-width apart and holding a barbell in the crook of your arms, near your belly. Your palms should be facing towards your body.
