Push through your heels to extend your hips and stand back up to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-zercher-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-barbell-zercher-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Assisted Bulgarian Split Squat', 'Grab a stick of some sort or hold onto something stable (rack, bench).
