Hold the stick in your right arm and put your right leg on the box.
Begin your squat by breaking at the knees. Get your knee close to the floor or all the way to the floor. Make sure to keep your chest tall.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-bodyweight-assisted-bulgarian-split-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-bodyweight-assisted-bulgarian-split-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Curtsy Lunge', 'Step your left foot diagonally behind your right leg, crossing it behind your body. Bend your knees and lower your hips until your left thigh is parallel to the floor and your right knee is hovering just above the ground.
Push through your right foot to straighten your legs and return to the starting position.
Repeat the movement with your other leg.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-bodyweight-curtsy-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-bodyweight-curtsy-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Forward Lunge', 'Step forward with one leg and lower your body until your front thigh is parallel to the floor and your back knee almost touches the ground. Keep your chest up and your front foot flat on the floor.
Push through your front foot to straighten your legs and return to the starting position.
Repeat the movement with your other leg.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-bodyweight-forward-lunge-front_zb4K50d.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-bodyweight-forward-lunge-side_4k0dfH0.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Heels Up Squat', 'Place your heels on a plate or very low step.
