Push through your right heel to straighten your right leg and return to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-forward-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-forward-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Dumbbell Goblet Bulgarian Split Squat', 'Holding the dumbbell in a goblet squat place your foot on a bench or box.
