Push through your front leg explosively to get back to your starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-goblet-forward-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-goblet-forward-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Dumbbell Goblet Lateral Lunge', 'Engage your core by drawing your belly button towards your spine. This will help to stabilize your body. Hold a dumbbell in a goblet position.
