Push your hips back and break at the knees.
Hit parallel depth and then drive through your heels back to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-front-rack-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-front-rack-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Dumbbell Goblet Pulse Squat', 'Hold a dumbbell in goblet position.
Squat down to parallel depth and then halfway back up.
Stay in this short range of motion for the duration of the set.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-goblet-pulse-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-goblet-pulse-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Dumbbell Heels Up Goblet Squat', 'Take a half kneeling stance. The dumbbell should start over your knee that is up.
