Begin your squat by pushing your hips back and breaking at the knees. Try to keep your chest tall while squatting.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-heels-up-narrow-goblet-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-dumbbell-heels-up-narrow-goblet-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Dumbbell Leg Extension', 'Place a dumbbell between your feet. Lean back slightly and hold on to the bench.
