Go as low as you can while keeping your heels flat on the ground, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Squat Reach', 'Stand holding a weight plate at chest height with both hands.
Lower into a squat, extending the plate in front of you at chest height
As you stand back up, pull the plate back into your chest.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-reach-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-reach-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Squat Hold Reach', 'Hold the plate with both hands at chest height.
