Hold the squat position and reach the plate forward, keeping your arms straight and your back straight.
Return the plate to your chest while you hold the squat position and repeat reaching the plate in front of you', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-hold-reach-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-hold-reach-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Curtsy Lunge', 'Stand with feet shoulder-width apart and the plate in front of the torso.
