Push through the front foot to return to the starting position.
Repeat on the other side by stepping back and across with the left foot.
Continue alternating sides for desired reps.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-curtsy-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-curtsy-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Squat Hold Curl', 'Lower into a squat position, keeping the plate at chest height.
Slowly curl the plate towards your shoulders, keeping your elbows close to your body.
Hold for a moment at the top of the curl before lowering the plate back to chest height.
Repeat the curls as you hold the squat position.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-hold-curl-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-squat-hold-curl-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Lateral Lunge', 'Stand with feet hip-width apart and the plate held in front of the torso.
Take a step to the side with one foot, bending the knee and lowering the hips into a lunge.
Push through the front foot to return to the starting position.
Repeat on the other side by stepping to the other side with the other foot.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-lateral-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-lateral-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Forward Lunge', 'Stand with feet hip-width apart and the plate held in front of the torso.
Take a step forward with one foot, bending the front knee to lower the hips into a lunge.
Push through the front foot to return to the starting position.
Repeat on the other side by stepping forward with the other foot.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-forward-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-forward-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Single Leg Deadlift', 'Engage your core and straighten your legs to lift the plate off the ground.
