Keep your back straight and maintain a neutral head position while looking straight ahead.
Lower the plate back down to the ground while keeping your balance on one leg.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-single-leg-deadlift-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-single-leg-deadlift-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Reverse Lunge Twist', 'Step back with your right foot into a lunge position, both knees bent at 90 degrees.
