Push through your front foot to return to the starting position and repeat on the other side.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-reverse-lunge-twist-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-reverse-lunge-twist-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Reverse Lunge', 'Hold the plate at chest height close to your body
