Repeat the movement on the other side, stepping backwards with your right leg and lowering your body until your right thigh is parallel to the ground and your left knee is bent at a 90-degree angle.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-reverse-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-reverse-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Band Leg Extension', 'Anchor a band to something stable and set up a bench.
