Flex and extend your knees.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-band-leg-extension-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-band-leg-extension-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Overhead Squat', 'Hold a weight plate at arms length overhead, with your arms fully extended. The plate should be directly above your head and your elbows should be locked.
