Once your thighs are parallel to the ground or as low as you can go, pause for a moment.
Push through your heels to return to a standing position, keeping the weight plate overhead the entire time.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-overhead-squat-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-overhead-squat-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Deficit Lunge', 'Stand on a plate with both feet.
