Push through your front leg until both feet are back on the plate.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-deficit-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-deficit-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Overhead Walking Lunge', 'Stand tall with a plate overhead.
