Go back to a standing position and then step forward with the opposing legs.', 'quads', '{https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-overhead-walking-lunge-front.mp4,https://media.musclewiki.com/media/uploads/videos/branded/male-plate-overhead-walking-lunge-side.mp4}') ON CONFLICT(name) DO NOTHING;INSERT INTO exercise (name, description, category, videos) VALUES('Plate Squat Hold', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, with a weight plate held in both hands at chest height.
